        "about_title": "The Artist",
        "blog_10_content": "<p class=\"mb-6 leading-relaxed font-light text-zinc-400\"><span></span><strong class=\"text-zinc-200 font-medium\">Speed is a feature.</strong><span> Every second of delay in page load time leads to significant drop-offs in conversion rates.</span></p>",
        "blog_10_title": "The Impact of Site Speed on UX",
        "blog_11_content": "<p class=\"mb-6 leading-relaxed font-light text-zinc-400\"><span></span><strong class=\"text-zinc-200 font-medium\">The world is mobile.</strong><span> With over half of global web traffic originating from mobile devices, a mobile-first approach is no longer optional.</span></p>",
        "blog_11_title": "Designing for Mobile-First Audiences",
        "blog_12_content": "<p class=\"mb-6 leading-relaxed font-light text-zinc-400\"><span></span><strong class=\"text-zinc-200 font-medium\">The battle of modern UI styles.</strong><span> While Neumorphism mimics extruded plastic, Glassmorphism brings a sense of depth and translucency.</span></p>",
