        "blog_15_title": "Lovable: AI-Powered App Building",
        "blog_16_content": "<p class=\"mb-6 leading-relaxed font-light text-zinc-400\"><strong class=\"text-zinc-200 font-medium\">An agentic coding companion.</strong> Claude Code lives in your terminal, understands your entire codebase, and executes multi-step tasks autonomously.</p>",
        "blog_16_title": "Claude Code: The Terminal AI Agent",
