        "blog_17_title": "Antigravity: Google's Agentic Coder",
        "blog_18_content": "<p class=\"mb-6 leading-relaxed font-light text-zinc-400\"><strong class=\"text-zinc-200 font-medium\">The IDE wars have entered a new era.</strong> Cursor and Windsurf are redefining what code editors can do with deep AI integration and agentic workflows.</p>",
        "blog_18_title": "Cursor vs. Windsurf: AI Editor Battle",
